100 is perfect in that category, maybe 1-2 total in the sport (wilder power, russell speed)

97-99 ATG/HOF level talent

92-97 P4P (around 10 in the sport)

87-92 elite (handful in the best divisions, rare in the lesser ones, top 30 P4P) 

82-87 world class (quality guys, fringe-elite)

77-82 championship level fighters (top 5ish)

72-77 contender level fighters (top 15ish)

70-77 fringe contenders (top 15-30ish)

60-70 gatekeepers (top 50-100ish)

40-60 journeymen (top 200ish)

20-40 club fighters/trial horses

0-20 tomato can/Palooka (paid to lose)

